trans-unit.source: Specifies the page size or roll width of the paper or other print media.
trans-unit.target: 指定的页大小或卷的纸张或其他打印介质的宽度。

trans-unit.source: This enumeration is used to provide values for the <xref:System.Printing.PageMediaSize.PageMediaSizeName%2A> property.

The <xref:System.Printing.PageMediaSize> class, in turn, is used to provide values for the <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A> property where it specifies the various page sizes a printer can use, and the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.PageMediaSize%2A> property, where it instructs a printer which page size to use.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Printing.PageMediaSize>类，反过来，用于提供的值<xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A>属性，它指定的各页上可以使用打印机的大小和<xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.PageMediaSize%2A>属性，它指示哪些页面大小，以使用打印机的位置。</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.PageMediaSize%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PageMediaSize>
